name: IU / Lee Ji-Eun
description:
Check out this My BMAC Page for more LORAs

First Lora i make based on 20 photos.

Works well with 2.5D models but not really well with photorealistic models.

Doesn't have any trigger words, just use "1girl" prompt

Recommended Settings:

Weight: 0.5-0.8

Sampler: DPM 2M++ Karras, DPM SDE Karras

Use hires.fix

if you're using realistic models like chilloutmix recommended use prompt: detailed face, perfect skin, white skin, bright skin. And use lower CFG Scale and sampling steps

Please review and leave a suggestion on how to improve this Lora. Thank you


It is prohibited to use this Lora to make NSFW/18+ images
